{"tid":1749524,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！？高票率唔係贏撚緊呀，好撚多鬼票出現！","createTime":"2019-11-24T04:08:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T05:13:23.000Z","uid":78612,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"04bd4c3a731ba35ea2f82204eb7eda06c96f6ae6","tid":1749524,"uid":78612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"一車又一車種票黨來了 <br />\n<br />\n寶馬山選區閩橋中學票站，一車又一車的大陸人樣種票黨集合，每組十四到十六人，呢班人先影一張大合照證明開工，我質問自由黨候選人阮建中，他及團隊一句也不敢回應，自由黨邵家輝就是在立法會高調反對獨立調查。見我影相，所有人立即擰塊面埋牆￼。<br />\n<br />\n￼如果你唔嚟投票，等於支持警暴，殘害香港人，今日你被打，不等如安全。香港人不要再食催淚彈，大家出嚟投票，為自己為下一代。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/642515382497502/posts/2651795198236167?d=n&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F642515382497502%2Fposts%2F2651795198236167%3Fd%3Dn%26sfns%3Dmo&d=s93SzOo3lOnuHTfFtNogbQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=753ce75c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/642515382497502/posts/2651795198236167?d=n&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNuEaLr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNuEaLr.jpg&h=d98d0ae4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚輕敵呀，逼多幾個fd去投票呀！</span></span>"},{"pid":"56251be39f22e3a938ae224105e1d141d4e94697","tid":1749524,"uid":16109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"00b6f6fcfbd8f8635578541cfc8a7010ceb10c2e","tid":1749524,"uid":18639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"【突發】英國上議院議員來香港監督選舉，有異樣請FB舉報<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1746728\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1746728</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ca5d96e1fd5faa66ae5a223248b2fa8ca8c1f1bf","tid":1749524,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T04:39:26.000Z","msg":"RTHK鏗鏘集：如有任何選舉異常情況 請向91829284報